She kissed HotRod, "Hmmm, Honey is something I could get used to." 
She kissed him again.

::Battera::
She was healing in the CR chamber from the stab wound to her abdoman.


::KitKat::
She trembled and mumbled in her sleep as Phobia carried her,"Yes.  
hmmmm....yes."


::Spears::
She nuzzled against Prebon and sighed, "Yes, please do me that favor, 
master. You be the one to hold me hostage. I trust you."  SHe reached 
up and kissed him again.

::SnowCat::
She unloaded the supplies and then walked up to Ramulus. "You look 
like you could use a CR yourself." She chuckled, "How was the flight? 
A little rough?" She smiled and smirked."I never knew bots could look 
a little pale."
